<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>zhōng guó xīn 迦南134</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 yuǎn gé qiān shān wàn shuǐ níng jù yī gè zhōng guó xīn xīn xīn xiāng yìn qí xīn nǔ lì xìng wàng fú yīn
 shén ài zhōng guó gèng ài wǒ men zài zhè lǐ zài nà lǐ zhǎo dào wǒ men zhè qún rén
 shí zhōng měi fēn měi miǎo cóng méi yǒu tíng liú chuán fú yīn de huǒ yàn shí kè rán shāo zài xīn tóu
 jiǎo bù jí cōng cōng tà shàng zhēng chéng shēn pī yuè sè tóu dǐng fán xīng
 yào gěi nà hēi àn de máo wū diǎn liàng yī zhǎn xīn dēng gěi nà wǔ shí liù gè mín zú dài qù hé píng
 wǒ men yōng yǒu yī kē chì chéng de zhōng guó xīn ài mín zú ài tóng bāo ài de shàng de měi yī gè rén</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>134</hymn_number>
</song>